Here there are several different student housing, in mixed sizes

4
00:00:13,658 --> 00:00:15,582
Depending on how you want to live.

5
00:00:15,582 --> 00:00:19,276
You can, among other things, live in corridor with shared kitchen and living room,

6
00:00:19,276 --> 00:00:22,324
in a collective or in a separate apartment.

7
00:00:23,638 --> 00:00:27,025
There are both student apartments but also ordinary rental properties

8
00:00:27,025 --> 00:00:29,454
Around Örebro.

9
00:00:29,454 --> 00:00:33,008
This is how it may seem to live in one near campus.

10
00:00:33,008 --> 00:00:35,033
In this student housing lives Isabelle,

11
00:00:35,033 --> 00:00:39,932
Like all her neighbors, stay here because they are plugging in the university.

12
