Here Jacob lives with his partner Sofie

29
00:01:44,934 --> 00:01:47,669
Both moved here from Stockholm when they started plugging.

30
00:01:47,669 --> 00:01:50,967
Their apartment is a third of 65 square meters

31
00:01:50,967 --> 00:01:53,652
And costs about SEK 8,400 a month.

32
00:01:56,000 --> 00:02:00,055
What Jacob likes best with the area is the tranquility and proximity to nature.

33
00:02:00,752 --> 00:02:02,687
As you understand, there are several different ways

34
00:02:02,687 --> 00:02:04,238
Living as a student in Örebro.

35
00:02:05,909 --> 00:02:09,077
But how have the students gone about getting these apartments?

36
00:02:09,077 --> 00:02:11,462
Here are some tips on how to get hold of a home

37
00:02:11,462 --> 00:02:13,780
before or at the beginning of your studies.

38
00:02:14,534 --> 00:02:16,377
You can stand in a residential queue

39
00:02:16,377 --> 00:02:19,379
At, among other things, the municipal housing company Öbo

40
00:02:19,379 --> 00:02:21,781
or with other private landlords.

41
00:02:21,781 --> 00:02:24,343
In Örebro it is free to stand in a residential queue,

42
00:02:24,343 --> 00:02:26,975
and you can queue up before you seek education,

43
00:02:26,975 --> 00:02:28,268
So do it now.

44
00:02:28,268 --> 00:02:31,651
Some private landlords do not use a queuing system

45
00:02:31,651 --> 00:02:34,806
Without it, it is important to be first come, first served with a statement of interest.

46
00:02:35,540 --> 00:02:40,110
On Örebro Municipality's website there is a list of all private landlords.

47
00:02:41,235 --> 00:02:44,880
If you would probably not find any apartment in time until the course starts

48
00:02:44,880 --> 00:02:47,772
So Öbo has a so -called housing guarantee.

49
00:02:47,772 --> 00:02:50,381
This means that you who fail to find any apartment

50
00:02:50,381 --> 00:02:52,613
may receive a time -limited agreement

51
00:02:52,613 --> 00:02:56,470
So that you have somewhere to live during the first semester of your studies.

52
00:02:56,470 --> 00:03:00,470
Read more about how the housing guarantee works at obo.se.

53
